# 发布课程 [POST /chapter/add]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
|---|---|---|---|
|title|Y|String||
|intro|N|String||
|content|Y|String||
|free|Y|Integer|0 收费 1免费|
|duration|Y|Long|学习时长(ms)|
|lessonId|Y|Long|专辑id|
|cover|Y|String|封面|
|coverSize|Y|String|50*50|

+ Request (application/json)
  {
    "phone": "15210607694",
    "password": "register"
  }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
      "c": 0,
      "m": "",
      "d": {
          "chapterId":1
      }
  }


# 课程详情 [GET /chapter/detail]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
|---|---|---|---|
|chapterId|Y|Long||

+ Parameters
    + chapterId:1910300 (required,int) - 课程ID

+ Request (application/json)
  {
    "phone": "15210607694",
    "password": "register"
  }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
      "c": 0,
      "m": "",
      "d": {
          "access":0,//0 有权限访问 1 无权限访问
          "pricePreMonth":"1.00",
          "chapter":{
                    "课程结构体"
          }
      }
  }


# 课程列表 [POST /chapter/list]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
|---|---|---|---|
|free|N|Integer|0 收费 1 免费 不传查所有|
|time|N|Long|翻页数据||
|lessonId|Y|Long||

+ Request (application/json)
