  }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  {
      "c": 0,
      "m": "",
      "d": {
          "list":[
              {
                  "课程结构体"
              }
          ]
      }
  }


# 点赞 [POST /chapter/like]

|参数|必选|类型|参数说明|
